* [[突角小粉蝶|突角小粉蝶]] ''[[Leptidea_amurensis|Leptidea amurensis]]'' {{small|(Ménétriès, 1859)}}{{r|zgdwz|page1=360}}
* [[杜波小粉蝶|杜波小粉蝶]] ''L. duponcheli''
* [[圆翅小粉蝶|圆翅小粉蝶]] ''[[Leptidea_gigantea|Leptidea gigantea]]'' {{small|(Leech, 1890)}}{{r|zgdwz|page1=364}}
* ''L. juvernica''
* [[乳色小粉蝶|乳色小粉蝶]] ''L. lactea''
* [[莫氏小粉蝶|莫氏小粉蝶]] ''[[Leptidea_morsei|Leptidea morsei]]'' {{small|Fenton, 1881}}{{r|zgdwz|page1=362}}
* [[雷小粉蝶|雷小粉蝶]] ''L. reali''
* [[锯纹小粉蝶|锯纹小粉蝶]] ''[[Leptidea_serrata|Leptidea serrata]]'' {{small|Lee, 1955}}{{r|zgdwz|page1=361}}
* [[条纹小粉蝶|条纹小粉蝶]] ''[[Leptidea_sinapis|Leptidea sinapis]]'' {{small|(Linnaeus, 1758)}}{{r|zgdwz|page1=363}}

